# Cursor Rules — linum-core-portfolio

<!-- BEGIN linum-govern -->
## linum-govern Governance Active

This project is governed by **linum-govern**. All code changes are audited for:

- Architecture alignment (`.claude/linum-govern/docs/architecture/`)
- Code style compliance (`.claude/linum-govern/docs/rules/`)
- Validation contract adherence (`.claude/linum-govern/docs/contracts/`)
